Poll: Ruling Union of Peasants and Greens of Lithuania tops the rating of parties again
The Union of Peasants and Greens of Lithuania, which heads the ruling coalition of the Diet, topped the rating of the parties.
This was shown by a poll conducted by the sociological research company Vilmorus for the time being ordered by the newspaper Lietuvos rytas.
